{"tid":175470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朱經緯案拖逾850日 據悉警方快將提控","createTime":"2017-03-27T13:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T13:48:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e0e5561bcd68dc2ff63679d99232b38ccf2a083","tid":175470,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:38:09.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170327/56488265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170327%2F56488265&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f79e08c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170327%2F56488265&h=4fd96363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170327/56488265</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\nlink 入邊有片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n朱經緯案拖逾850日 據悉警方快將提控<br />\n<br />\n35,797<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0327 20:34<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n退休警司朱經緯涉縑在傘運期間，用警棍胡亂毆打旺角途人，案發至今超過850日，律政司和警方至今仍未決定是否提控。《蘋果》接獲消息指，警方快將檢控朱經緯，但未知會起訴哪些罪名等詳情；無綫新聞則引述消息，稱朱經緯今晚會被「預約拘捕」。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》亦引述消息指，律政司本月初已向警方提交文件，建議起訴朱經緯毆打，警方今日通知朱經緯回警署，他將被控「毆打導致他人受傷」，日內上庭。惟有線新聞指，「襲擊致造成身體傷害罪」只是律政司建議起訴朱經緯的其中一個選擇，警方有考慮以此罪名起訴，但未有透露最終決定。「襲擊致造成身體傷害罪」是來自《侵害人身罪條例》第39條（俗稱「傷人39」），最高可判監禁3年。<br />\n<br />\n今年2月初，受害人Osman鄭仲恒的代表律師向律政司司長袁國強發公開信，表明由2月9日起計2個月內，若律政司仍不提控，他們將全力支援Osman以一切合法方式維護公義，包括私人檢控。警方當時回覆稱一直與律政司保持溝通，投訴警察課亦有跟進有關事項。<br />\n<br />\n退休警司朱經緯在2014年11月底傘運期間，涉嫌以警棍胡亂毆打途人鄭仲恒，根據監警會的文件，朱經緯曾辯稱自己以警棍作為「手臂延伸」拍打投訴人，驅使他向前行。即使連監警會事隔2年多後，都認為投訴成立，但律政司仍遲遲未提出起訴。<br />\n<br />\n為重溫朱經緯當日拍打投訴人行為，《蘋果》再次將當晚攝影記者，於亞皆老街近彌敦道所得警方驅趕人群時的片段，一刀不剪播出，讓各位讀者自行判斷朱經緯是「毆打途人」還是「以警棍作為手臂延伸」拍打投訴人。  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n【食晏大晒】午飯時間開記招 國足拒絕出席<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n【清算傘運】官媒指戴耀廷等人「佔中三醜」 粵撐佔中者周五宣判"},{"pid":"982eb5ad94087871fc5d23625a5a2fbcba88f7cc","tid":175470,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170327/large/1490617971_0382.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170327%2Flarge%2F1490617971_0382.jpg&h=faf9312a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7687234b09d86e884b1fa04d0fa7a762c80dbbe","tid":175470,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:44:39.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170327/56488265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170327%2F56488265&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f79e08c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170327%2F56488265&h=4fd96363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170327/56488265</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\nlink 入邊有片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話,  我屌老母,  真係衝埋去亂打嗰喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b9f3c2610d01690a31248480b77c785f049bd8","tid":175470,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T13:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[url]<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170327/56488265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170327%2F56488265&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f79e08c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170327%2F56488265&h=4fd96363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170327/56488265</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\nlink 入邊有片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話,  我屌老母,  真係衝埋去亂打嗰喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n扑儍瓜咁"},{"pid":"540c9e6773b512b3584d2495669bb4307c736afc","tid":175470,"ui